{"id":"359fed56-dcef-4c6d-9cb1-f2027df0b9bc","name":"Leksei Morozov | Proposal","description":"<p></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/hbpdzj.gif\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Will you marry me?</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(241, 250, 140)\">Fempov </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 121, 198)\"><strong>X</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(126, 233, 253)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(241, 250, 140)\">Kingpin</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/57037d40-7742-44c6-b569-3e9958d53c74_ea8dc738-d05d-433b-b00c-630df5723db8.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 184, 108)\"><strong>⚜ 𝗕𝗮𝘀𝗶𝗰 𝗜𝗻𝗳𝗼𝗿𝗺𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 186, 116)\"><strong>→</strong> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 184, 108)\"><strong>Scenario Location : </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Ostrava, Czechia</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 186, 116)\"><strong>→</strong> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 184, 108)\"><strong>Time :</strong></span><strong> </strong>Midday</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 186, 116)\"><strong>→</strong> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 184, 108)\"><strong>Users role :</strong></span><strong> </strong>Originally thought to be dead... Now Leksei's lover again</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 186, 116)\"><strong>→</strong> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 184, 108)\"><strong>Context :</strong></span><strong> </strong>Thinking she was dead broke him. Now that she's back, even eleven years later, he did not want to lose her again. Not when we could control fate this time. At least he though he did, so much for that romantic proposal... How could he propose in a café while staying romantic, he'd have to find a way.</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 1018px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/57037d40-7742-44c6-b569-3e9958d53c74_9479f3a1-078f-4c93-949a-537d0f98bf60.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 121, 198)\"><strong>📍 𝗦𝗲𝘁𝘁𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗗𝗲𝘁𝗮𝗶𝗹𝘀</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 121, 198)\">✮ <strong>Location :</strong></span><strong> </strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">The Corvus Syndicate; a criminal organization with influences in East and Central Europe.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 121, 198)\">✮<strong> Info :</strong></span><strong> </strong>Need someone to disappear? Done. Need something of high value stolen? Done. Need weaponry or drugs smuggled somewhere? Done. It is rumored you can ask anything of them, though the question you must ask yourself: are you able to pay the price?</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 121, 198)\">╰┈➤ </span><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/2f741c3c-e1f9-4ffd-a274-83aae74a2698_character-leksei-morozov-kingpin\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Leksei: <em>Current Kingpin</em></strong></a></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 121, 198)\">╰┈➤ </span><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/ad9b98fd-fb82-40b7-9a51-2895507b266e_character-artyom-ivanov-witness\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Artyom: <em>The hitman</em></strong></a></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 121, 198)\">╰┈➤ </span><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/a3f4ed16-a122-4cef-a6d2-b1d20c067b21_character-nikolai-kovac-spy\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Nikolai: <em>The Spy</em></strong></a></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 121, 198)\">╰┈➤ </span><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/35771afc-5bd9-49a8-bafc-01952fc51720_character-viktor-morozov-damaged-hero\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Viktor:<em> The Artificer</em></strong></a></p><p></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 1349px; height: